        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Manors Golf Apparel continues to cement its reputation as a sportswear tastemaker with the launch of its SS25 'Drive to Nowhere' collection\u2014an ode to golf's most thrilling moments at the margins and the journeys we take to reach them. Whether chasing the sunset on an undiscovered course or embracing the raw unpredictability of the elements, MANORS ensures that golfers are equipped for a game played beyond the white stakes. The SS25 'Drive to Nowhere' collection is an invitation to explore the sport on your terms, embracing adventure wherever your drive may take you</p>"
          }
        }
      },
