        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Collection: Fusing Performance, Sustainability, and Style",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Tour Polo: Performance Beyond the Fairway</strong></h3><p>Inspired by endurance sports beyond the fairway, the <strong>Tour Polo</strong> channels the aesthetics of cycling while delivering peak golf performance. Constructed from <strong>Seawool\u00ae fabric</strong>, crafted from upcycled oyster shells and recycled plastic bottles, the polo offers cutting-edge functionality:</p><ul><li><strong>Moisture-wicking technology</strong> to keep you dry during high-intensity rounds.</li><li><strong>Odour control</strong> ensures freshness no matter how long your game extends.</li><li><strong>UV 50+ protection</strong>, shielding you from harsh sun exposure.</li><li><strong>Quarter zip placket</strong> for versatile wear and a contemporary look.</li><li><strong>Statement back branding</strong> that elevates its bold, modern design.</li></ul><p>For players who push boundaries and go the distance, the Tour Polo is a must-have addition to the wardrobe.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
