    "text_3": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3><strong>Frontier Tailored Shirt: Effortless Transition from Course to Clubhouse</strong></h3><p>Blurring the line between technical golfwear and everyday elegance, the <strong>Frontier Tailored Shirt</strong> is designed with lightweight, <strong>4-way stretch, water-resistant fabric</strong> that adapts to every movement on the course. Key features include:</p><ul><li><strong>A refined chest pocket</strong>, offering subtle storage for tees or scorecards.</li><li><strong>A concealed placket</strong> enhances its sleek, modern aesthetic.</li><li><strong>Multi-functional wear</strong>, perfect as a layering piece or standalone top.</li></ul><p>The Frontier Tailored Shirt embodies sophistication without sacrificing performance\u2014ideal for golfers who demand style and utility in equal measure.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
