    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h3>Greenskeeper Trousers & Shorts: The Evolution of a MANORS Classic </h3><p>A new chapter in the <strong>Greenskeeper series</strong>, the <strong>Chino Greenskeeper Trousers & Shorts</strong> merge <strong>classic tailoring</strong> with <strong>on-course functionality</strong>. Crafted from <strong>Primeflex\u2122 fabric</strong>, they offer:</p><ul><li><strong>Durability and water resistance</strong>, ensuring resilience against the elements.</li><li><strong>2-way stretch</strong>, providing unrestricted movement during every swing.</li><li><strong>A buttery-soft hand feel</strong>, maintaining the luxurious comfort of a traditional chino.</li><li><strong>Double pleats</strong> enhance the silhouette for a refined look.</li><li><strong>A simplified ticket pocket</strong>, thoughtfully designed to hold a scorecard securely.</li></ul><p>With the addition of two new colourways, this release expands MANORS' commitment to bridging traditional golf wear with contemporary, versatile styling.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
