    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "The Campaign: A Road Trip Through the Golfing Wilderness",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The <strong>SS25 'Drive to Nowhere' collection</strong> is brought to life through a stunning visual campaign, featuring MANORS ambassadors <strong>ShortSide, Ben Kolde, Josh Park, and DJ Rhetorik</strong>. Their journey took them across <strong>Arizona's breathtaking landscapes</strong>, from <strong>Phoenix to the Grand Canyon and through the Navajo Nation in Monument Valley</strong>.</p><p>Captured by <strong>LA-based sports and fashion photographer Kris Ryan</strong> and long-time MANORS collaborator <strong>Douglas Skupien</strong>, the campaign blurs the boundaries between sport, adventure, and culture. Against the surreal red rock formations and open-road vistas, the <strong>'Drive to Nowhere'</strong> collection embodies the spirit of golf as a game of limitless exploration.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
