    "text_7": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "About MANORS Golf Apparel",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>MANORS is redefining golfwear for a new generation. Inspired by the sport's rich history but driven by the evolution of modern players, MANORS is more than just apparel\u2014it's an ethos. Rooted in performance, style, and sustainability, the brand continues to push the boundaries of what golf fashion can be.</p><p>The SS25 'Drive to Nowhere' collection is now available exclusively at <a href=\"https://trendygolf.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://trendygolf.com/\"><strong>TRENDYGOLF</strong></a>. Experience golf beyond the white stakes\u2014explore the collection today.</p><p>Campaign video assets are credited to <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/dougguillot/?hl=en\" target=\"_blank\">Douglas Guillot</a> and campaign photography assets are credited to <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/krisryanphoto/\" target=\"_blank\">Kris Ryan.</a></p>"
          }
        }
      },
